Problem Statement – Practical 1 
Student Profile Viewer App – A Basic Android Application Using Activities, Services, and User Interface Components 
You are required to design and develop an Android application named Student Profile Viewer. The objective of this practical is to help students understand the basic components of 
Android such as Activities, Services, Content Providers, basic User Interface elements, and working with an Android Virtual Device (AVD) and USB Debugging. 
        Procedure: 
        Open Android Studio. 
        Click File → New → New Project. 
        Select Empty Views Activity. 
        Name: StudentProfileViewer 
        Package Name: package com.example.studentprofileviewer 
        Language: Java 
        Minimum SDK: API 21 (Android 5.0) 
        Click Finish. 
